william s. burroughs : a man within is a 2010 independent american documentary film directed by yony leyser about william s. burroughs , featuring previously unreleased footage and interviews with his friends and colleagues .   the film uses archival footage and interviews with john waters , patti smith , iggy pop , gus van sant , genesis breyer p-orridge , sonic youth , laurie anderson , amiri baraka , jello biafra , and david cronenberg .   the film is narrated by peter weller , with a soundtrack by patti smith and sonic youth .